rows.label: qst101804_msg001
rows.name: LIST_QST101804仮実装

rows.label: qst101804_msg002
rows.name: ジゾーのことなんて忘れたいも

rows.label: qst101804_msg0001
rows.name: Vahsah! Jizo find you at last!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0002
rows.name: Huh? Who are you?

rows.label: qst101804_msg0003
rows.name: Jizo! Lost a bit of weight...

rows.label: qst101804_msg0004
rows.name: Nahhhh, you can't fool me!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0005
rows.name:
Jizo got defeated at Badfella's
Cave Fort. I saw him stop moving
and everything...

rows.label: qst101804_msg0006
rows.name:
Are you trying to taunt a poor guy
grieving over his dead Driver...?

rows.label: qst101804_msg0007
rows.name: Huh? And who might you be...?

rows.label: qst101804_msg0008
rows.name: You brought Jizo here? Really?

rows.label: qst101804_msg0009
rows.name:
...Well, I'll be damned. I can feel
Jizo's resonance! It really is you!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0010
rows.name:
That just like silly old Vahsah...
Forget all about Jizo.

rows.label: qst101804_msg0011
rows.name:
Of course Jizo not dead! Otherwise
Vahsah back to Core Crystal already!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0012
rows.name:
Oh, right. Good point.
Wait, but then...aw, crap.

rows.label: qst101804_msg0013
rows.name:
I've been spending a TON of money
here. Trying to enjoy my last moments,
y'know. But if you're still alive...

rows.label: qst101804_msg0014
rows.name:
Silly Vahsah should know better!
Even if Vahsah lose memories,
somebody would remember debts!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0015
rows.name: Hahaha... You're probably right!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0016
rows.name:
Yeah, um, I might be in a
spot of trouble.

rows.label: qst101804_msg0017
rows.name: See that old lady?

rows.label: qst101804_msg0018
rows.name:
I kinda promised her I wouldn't leave
town till I paid back everything I owe.

rows.label: qst101804_msg0019
rows.name: Why Vahsah make promise like that?!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0020
rows.name:
Well, I thought you were done for, and
I'd be disappearing soon, so...I figured
it didn't matter what I did any more!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0021
rows.name:
OK. No need to worry.
Everything be OK.

rows.label: qst101804_msg0022
rows.name:
Jizo keep little bit of coin tucked
away to cover silly mistakes by Vahsah.

rows.label: qst101804_msg0023
rows.name:
Funds hidden safely in treasure box
near Funnystone Highway.

rows.label: qst101804_msg0024
rows.name:
Da-yum.
I knew I could count on my Driver!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0025
rows.name: Meh-heh-heh!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0026
rows.name:
Driver and Blade must support each
other. That golden rule of relationship.

rows.label: qst101804_msg0027
rows.name:
Some folks say we're a bit of
a strange pair, though...

rows.label: qst101804_msg0028
rows.name:
Please, friends... Will you help Jizo
get to little money hoard?

rows.label: qst101804_msg0029
rows.name:
Thanks for helping Jizo. I really
appreciate it.

rows.label: qst101804_msg0030
rows.name:
Vahsah, wait here quietly.
Not spend money or make fuss!

rows.label: qst101804_msg0031
rows.name: Yessir! You can count on me!
